    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "not necessarily part of the API, but it would be good if we saved the \"default state\" of a widget as `undefined`, which won't get serialised by `qs`, as well as making page 1-indexed (rather than 0-indexed). That way `?p=2` will behave like you'd expect and will only get added once you go to the next page",
