  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "After discussing with @vvo, we came up with:\r\n - `routing` as the name of the feature\r\n - `router` as the name of the pluggable element that writes and read\r\n - `mapping` can be `stateMapping` (so that's it's not too generic) and the methods could be named:\r\n   - `stateToRoute`\r\n   - `routeToState`\r\n - let's keep `write`\r\n - and we keep the rest of @vvo proposal",
